&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.6765625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNhziagiapqea8GfaiakDg1ygHCp5VylkZfqHGAnSFatIN7hh1L1PU5C3bQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNS8OTojjBUFZg5rvx5X8ibkib21PT2varutyZ2lQYWPyibjgUwPUx7NlTw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;圆桥由5个圆形的平台串联而成，其宽大的桥面能够支持人们走路，骑车，跑步，散步，同时具有弧度的边界能够提供各种看城市的角度。每天将有5000人穿过此桥。Olafur Eliasson希望该桥的锯齿边缘可以降低行人通行速度，并且在此聚会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5734375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN6PboJ3q81EOKYs0HfiaPeZctFdHvZIcRm1ic1IgpXiazAnRTa5k5RkV8A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNRdz5z02EYgqQobH273tuMhicJRI7n5ftGQORnUaPXhMIzWrrLoiblAyA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.7765625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNH5jia65BZJcs326aq3FIZKfVzDGicfPM4X2Lu2jxEwjHSTGrtYyk4icCw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;指环天桥在两侧都提供了人行道和自行车道，能满足人们多样的需求。指环的内侧还集成了残疾人电梯系统，充分照顾到每一位身体不方便的朋友。其次，这设计还充分考虑到了之后的广告需求，整个指环的外壳可以定制，各种广告主或者机构可以对接展示他们的理念与产品。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7984375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNaPNeRnMbRUKkN8teKdtxWib9QFyxLMMsFCPdOepHEeicnXPQ9hagtM5g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7984375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNMhhWAiayDUIuXWgXD67g5wF0Sgic0Uabjz6MaqJpFbIXsS5Dro2daUhQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7984375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNETUTPymuiakfxR9X7hlOCPTENXBPyaOlupHRb1X4knUNGSoqwCAaCWA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;莫比乌斯环衍生桥在视觉和理论的基础上,这座桥是一个畅通无阻的莫比乌斯环,兼具了数学的理性与艺术的美感,桥体占据良好地段,可以观赏鹿特丹的天际线和饱览无限长空。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.765625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNxqvh1rAeLNm4zXMibuVqG1Wau3ZowFejAFA54CjPhRWbfAEIrrrCq8g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.70625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNLetpySiaQkSBSWibOJG4hiaQgVhUCQ8TWjXMpa86SSIVJb0op8qF7gAhw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNdPjdobXqH7B1tm0k9Y9mz1gn80Ypkp6T0oYy4kw84w1R1Pns3naJXQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4296875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN1lfvOReHQspoGQ7iaw8UTXud9XYHlicpFVKOc4mREs4amyKldbC1YaaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8953125&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNv5Uq8MfZN1lejc8rvwpZNUZhH1CW1jUBhKxqsLrSvPynIvU2vNXdjw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8734375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNaHENNr7sMZMFRa8gIX6GdJialVjIibk1S71jnPPiaaNkLB6bmsDzkZkDA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;在张家界的西边修建一条包括连桥和亭子的新旅途。这个设计如魔术一般梦幻神秘，其几何形态与复杂的景观形成鲜明的对比，如同被精心安置在景观上的浮雕。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNNr2RaiaMFAvkma2icSQWCiclmRU9NUAyzbEBGqytgIF2OWWXSf0GaRDWQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

