&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNyGo8M90RNPziasjktt5S2Nx7K11xeYYooFdAmPdW7vHc6hQ4fy0K50A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;该项目一个由983米的前高架桥改造而来的花园公共空间。废弃高架桥重生变为一条空中花园走廊，200多个当地品种的树木, 花草形成一条 “植物图书馆” 通道, 供行人和游客驻足游憩。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNclWMtTQJibb88fvKjib50rHWr2UPHtRsCgaE9HMnFNKsDKyJiaw8DlZibg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNdsbnG8kXI9cYau9SudIq2yTk7f5AteJEuhIMUeK8x26pVSWnFKC1Pw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN67I0h3YG1ag9ctBAKbdkib6vVSaCPgYuvbmLhVbet5XHKicakoJbJeug/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;“Bostanlı人行桥”弥补了沿海长廊流线中缺失的片断。通过其略呈弓形的纵截面和特别设计的梁，人行桥允许小型船只从其下通过，并向溪中的浮桥码头提供出入。建筑师为桥梁设计了不对称的横截面,允许游人坐着或躺着享受海湾优美的景色。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNwR59SPA2zsMmONkOtgYJ4EeXPIDaFadZR6tVnPQReM8kH9qslIRKTg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNNUym6Df0lM5icSgUq20KwjTXpfgxTsWgLs6C7F062L9cZtOTzLgbMVQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNEbpiaxekZZpibWWxdFQqFdmSCAynSich3OKECYr02OodcmADpYLSEk7AQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这座造型动感优美的混凝土人行天桥位于冰岛雷克雅未克首都新机场。混凝土壳体被设计的十分轻薄，弯曲的造型备具张力，桥柱相当细，整个桥体形态轻盈而灵活。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNxC4BB0KZhJSnU8ib7vExLAtKaEYyczlxjuafAu6XZiakyNg3IAWXkH5Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.628125&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNG6KxnoflRpjkx5LJRpqsic3Pc2HO6gTa2gfB9xuCjyCUEgCcWqKhCWQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNjI6uOd3YFxltcsmYeicwxMJ3xgFE4quPp4IiblXrh0ABlSYecbPR5nfw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;栖凤桥的理念采用的是一只展翅欲飞的凤凰，铺装设计采用简洁时尚的深灰色和浅灰色石材混铺，运用流线动感的线条来演绎，同时采用多种变形种植池，设置供人们休息的坐凳，在台阶两边分别以组团绿化作为边界，弱化台阶的生硬感。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNM6SHibv6gf3kMSibliclrYWFW0PerFlMueudWiccia3Z09L2Dzib6CCEIiaMg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNs5cJmjcGWib4Ub8N7WH5aOFWAtc1yDOk80SDsrXs6uKsDG5gHqD1V8Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNguN82560vB3FOicpgTDNOvuoXurRiadn4QZVNqO4bZhyzz0161mREknQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;在浦东开放的长达22公里的岸线中，“公共空间”是最核心的概念，在两座桥的设计中，都在尝试演绎一些几何形态上的变化，也充分考虑到与桥两端城市、景观环境的衔接。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNve4zbmEHCSxwuicE93zRlskUQPrcGdiajPWpSdemebdzuy6iaJiavLcibGw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNzBM2SiaPhvicmjdJbzHYwDFiaLiaLt77fyslNaFj438bribykTibKm2e9ibZg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNtTDmhbIrItB5Tpy6xll0CXS22McQO3Wnq5QYBhVX9P50VBWrziaVPEg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这个直径72米的圆环自行车交通天桥位于荷兰埃因霍温。其现代的设计，轻薄的体量和耀眼的灯光，如同飞蝶般，成为城市中让人振奋的交通新地标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.5&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNdskl28Jl1h8lheDTneDlUn2XZNMVNFZfZaZb2ticQXkoGRhAs2bGVMA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNWslqZP5sibD4WjmTNm2eMdnc6nSH7yvHTDARy6J2A8BiaDnexaUccqag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNQPF2s90dvNl41KetR7ia2YGu59iauMY3NfHtQzgT7d3d2D9sDr6OJtAQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这座桥全长130米，蜿蜒穿梭于树木和枝干之间。 桥梁大致呈新月形，分别有两处与森林地表接触，最高点有12米（约3层楼高），桥梁冲破树木，飞跃树梢，带来树顶观景的非凡感受，展现了开普敦城市和周围雄伟山脉的360度全景景观。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNicibp61AHDoTmq1BAGEupTQxorMEiaLULdB8TfyrQficb14wOQBXuaHAOQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7484375&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNzzS9w3BwkAKc7DCpFJR06wrk0ZEGa8CcZls8BicF7sHXTIJHdMkLqaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNicPmeHy7O9K1yKBgdBDacK0DW6Dp6tF0eIZCtN2W92T8EVr6XHvTCyg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这是一条让人震惊的8公里人行道木桥。整个人行道的设计不仅尽可能的对景观环境减少干扰，还为人们提供了一个戏剧性的观景体验。木桥紧贴河道延伸，跨越河流与悬崖，在山体上蜿蜒前进，到达山顶。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN8g9WJBvTXtQ7B0OHCXbk4gAMmkP1eIpTC2mJfjXADDDShVAOq6p2fA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNObu5uUk9jr5dHpHxuxGRJappiagboG3XzWXK6oC3HsQj7qXtpO6iahBA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNoia1l2WNhNnbqdafrRnUXnoorXHhrPTPKEOge4G37GRibYibgBeqr3uoA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;充气木桥漂浮在水面上，设计完全遵循“从摇篮到摇篮”的原则。桥梁利用下方的充气聚乙烯管道漂浮在水面上，不需要任何其他的结构支撑。经过处理后的固雅木具有很强的抗腐蚀能力，并能根据与水的接触程度灵活膨胀和收缩。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5140625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN5B50xeJDWfw25ib7HYibSwxKBF6Ce9MhgBYicaPe1TFRpqC88pFriaSOJQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6765625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYNkWKia6VQkZibiaGm55jRzcHW4TpwkR1ntvQ12u6RwkpG6am8IxTNmSWhg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/951TjTgiabkyurT7aotobopB5vicricHGYN32E2VQHo5XEic0q6o9qmvXwbtiaehDUCP5XOGwjdFXIAQdGjBzzbJB3Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Vlotwateringbrug桥，俗称“蝙蝠桥”，该桥由三个特定部分构成，为多个蝙蝠物种提供栖身之所。北面桥墩可作为蝙蝠越冬之处；桥身与砖石栏杆则供蝙蝠度过炎炎夏日。设计旨在为各类蝙蝠物种打造理想的栖息环境，以期扩大其种群数量。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

